&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;Cool&amp;#39;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The most appropriate&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;antonym&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of the given word&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;Seethed&amp;#39; is &amp;#39;Cool&amp;#39;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Let&amp;#39;s look at the meaning and examples of the given options:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 500px;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;tbody&gt;
