		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;E.g.&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;- A&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;group of women were &lt;strong&gt;cackling&lt;/strong&gt; in a corner.&lt;strong&gt;​&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;Option 1&lt;/strong&gt; i.e. &lt;strong&gt;dug up.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;The sentence indicates that her enthusiasm for philanthropy is clearly shown or supported by her actions in the community.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;The word &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;dug up&amp;quot;(&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;खोजना)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt; means to find something that has been hidden or forgotten, which fits the context of finding old documents in the attic.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;The words &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;dug out,&amp;quot; &amp;quot;dug in,&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;dug over&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; all convey different actions, making them incorrect choices based on the sentence&amp;#39;s context of finding old documents.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;Understanding the meaning of &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;dug up&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; in the context of the sentence helps to clarify that she found the old documents in the attic.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;Therefore, the&lt;strong&gt; correct answer&lt;/strong&gt; is- &lt;strong&gt;dug up&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dug out (&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;निकालना)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;means to remove something from a place where it is buried or covered.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dug in (&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;खुदाई करना)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;refers to making a defensive position by digging.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dug over (&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;जुताई करना)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;means to turn over soil in preparation for planting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;Option 4&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The primary issue in the sentence is to find the &lt;strong&gt;correct verb &lt;/strong&gt;that fits the context of the sentence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The sentence requires &lt;strong&gt;a verb &lt;/strong&gt;that fits with the action of initiating a strike.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The correct verb in this context is&lt;strong&gt; &amp;quot;called,&amp;quot; as in &amp;quot;called a strike.&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Therefore, the most appropriate option to fill the blank is&lt;strong&gt; &amp;quot;called.&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Therefore, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;Option 4&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Correct Sentence:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;&amp;quot;They &lt;strong&gt;called a strike&lt;/strong&gt; when the party members refused their plea.&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 1: &amp;quot;told&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;ndash; This option does not fit the context of initiating a strike.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 2: &amp;quot;behold&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;ndash; This option is not relevant to the context of the sentence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 3: &amp;quot;fallen&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;ndash; This option does not make sense in the context of the sentence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 4: &amp;quot;called&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;ndash; This is the&lt;strong&gt; correct &lt;/strong&gt;option as it fits the context of initiating a strike.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;The correct answer is&lt;strong&gt; Option 4 i.e. &amp;quot;keep his head&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;What should contextually fit in the blank: Remaining calm and composed.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;keep his head:&lt;/strong&gt; To stay calm in a stressful or difficult situation (तनावपूर्ण या मुश्किल स्थिति में शांत रहना)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li role=&quot;presentation&quot;&gt;This idiom is fitting because it implies maintaining composure and rationality amid chaos, indicating the person&amp;#39;s ability to stay calm when others might panic.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Therefore, the correct answer is &amp;quot;keep his head&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complete Sentence:&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;In the midst of chaos, he was the only one who could &lt;strong&gt;keep his head.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;bite the dust: &lt;/strong&gt;To fail or to be defeated (विफल होना या हारना)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;jump on the bandwagon:&lt;/strong&gt; To join others in doing something that is currently fashionable or successful (अन्य लोगों के साथ एक सफल या फैशनेबल चीज़ में शामिल होना)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;miss the mark:&lt;/strong&gt; To fail to achieve the intended goal (लक्ष्य को प्राप्त न करना)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;Schmuck&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Let us explore the marked&amp;nbsp;option:&amp;nbsp;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;Schmuck&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;a foolish or contemptible person&lt;/strong&gt;. (मूर्ख या अवमानना ​​करने वाला व्यक्ति)

		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;For example -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;The poor &lt;strong&gt;schmuck&lt;/strong&gt; next to you is paying full price for a second-hand phone&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
